---
title: Pan-Seared Calamari over Bulgur & Chorizo Hash with Parsley Gremolata
description: Never cooked calamari at home before? Worry not! A quick flash in a hot pan is all it takes to create perfectly tender rings. Served over peppery chorizo hash and topped with lemony parsley gremolata, think you'll be making this company-worthy dish more often.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/55097f4e6ced6ecc458b4569.jpg
